data.description: Stunning 3 bedroom+ FLEX Space, 2.5 Bath, upstairs laundry room. Two-Story home with versatile layout. This exquisite home currently utilized as a 5-bedroom haven, upstairs bonus area converted into two additional bedrooms with a removable partition wall, offering endless possibilities for customization to suit your lifestyle. The modern touch of Quartz countertops,Whirlpool stainless steel appliances in the open kitchen. The home is protected with impact windows. Nestled with a fenced yard, this sanctuary offers both privacy and security, with the added comfort of the screened patio, 22K whole house generator.  Two Tesla chargers, and an extra EV charger. Cutting edge solar panels to harness the power of the sun and lower energy cost.
